{"tid":2232256,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【無情】為縮減開支 阿仙奴炒吉祥物","createTime":"2020-10-06T09:15:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-06T16:14:14.000Z","uid":173952,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cb311ce57217b0c25d7598cb0f2e5de143cee1b9","tid":2232256,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T09:15:26.000Z","msg":"受到新冠肺炎疫情影響，大部分聯賽都要閉門作賽，令一眾球隊失去了可靠的門票收入，為了節省開支，英超球隊阿仙奴就決定辭退吉祥物 Gunnersaurus 的扮演者 Jerry Quy 。<br />\n<br />\n被球迷笑指是「清潔龍」的 Gunnersaurus 自 1993 年首次亮相，成為阿仙奴的吉祥物時，一直由 Jerry Quy 負責扮演， 27 年間 Jerry Quy 一直盡忠職守，落力炒熱球場內的氣氛，與球迷一同為球隊打氣，更試過因與賽事撞期而錯過了兄弟的婚禮。<br />\n<br />\n網上圖片<br />\n<br />\n由於疫情影響了球隊的門票收入，阿仙奴為了節省開支，認為沒有觀眾入場下 Gunnersaurus 的角色變得不重要，於是向這位老臣子派「大信封」，這個舉動引起不少球迷不滿，認為球隊太過沒有人情味，不過，球會強調 Gunnersaurus 一定會回歸。<br />\n<br />\n除了 Jerry Quy 外，阿仙奴於 8 月時已經裁走 55 名「職位重疊」員工，未知日後還會否向其他職員「開刀」。"},{"pid":"486f9d66f626bfd0dc2e29f3c175f95ee56470ae","tid":2232256,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T09:17:15.000Z","msg":"人情味<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"685ccdf0539fd2a3ba152bd7ebcba2f5d9b4c251","tid":2232256,"uid":30084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T09:29:08.000Z","msg":"炒一個後備球員可以頂幾多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e37bd70cbb306c2f114604a9f5e5e1af063d0d90","tid":2232256,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T11:11:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-U08sPkuFyzM/WzzuqFTG83I/AAAAAAAAVKM/VRHri9V0FO0hE1uXGjso3Y2fquFVkT2DwCLcBGAs/s1600/Illbeback.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-U08sPkuFyzM%2FWzzuqFTG83I%2FAAAAAAAAVKM%2FVRHri9V0FO0hE1uXGjso3Y2fquFVkT2DwCLcBGAs%2Fs1600%2FIllbeback.gif&h=f0b57664&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c778abc6d16424beaa91b0eb11b9d521eccb108b","tid":2232256,"uid":256796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T11:12